		<title>The Solo Cruisers — Coming Soon</title>
		<style>
			*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

			body {
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
